query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b) */ select count(*)
from so_user AS u1
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id AND u1.upvotes >= 1 AND u1.upvotes <= 100
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('apple',
'ru',
'salesforce')
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on s.site_id = tq1.site_id
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.name IN ('apex',
'c#',
'c++',
'html',
'java',
'javascript',
'macos',
'php',
'python')
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND q1.favorite_count >= 0 AND q1.favorite_count <= 1
inner join answer AS a1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.id = a1.question_id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id
inner join badge AS b
on b.user_id = u1.id AND s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.name IN ('Benefactor',
'Constituent',
'Enthusiast',
'Explainer',
'Peer Pressure',
'Promoter',
'Revival');
